{"tid":2286382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國：多名持英國NHS檢測報告赴華後確診 即日起不接受該檢測報告","createTime":"2020-11-15T03:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T02:15:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":105,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e169904dd192e2741ff2a87be25ba30af82fdd","tid":2286382,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"中國駐英使館：即日起不接受英國NHS檢測報告<br />\n<br />\n中國駐英國大使館指，即日起健康碼審核工作，不再接受英國衛生部門(NHS)發出的檢測報告，並決定要求檢測報告須有乘客個人信息，除姓名外，亦要包括出生日期或護照號碼、檢測機構地址、聯繫電話、電子郵箱、採樣時間、報告時間及檢測項目等，使領將隨機聯繫檢測機構核實報告真偽，對無法核實或核實為偽造，將不予核發綠色健康碼。<br />\n<br />\n使館表示，英國政府規定，NHS檢測不適用於國際旅行目的，近期多名自英國出發赴華的旅客，在抵達中國後確診，大部分持有NHS發出的檢測報告，指一般只有出現症狀人員才能預約NHS檢測，健康人士前往NHS檢測將面臨接觸感染者的可能，如受感染不單損害個人健康，產生經濟負擔，更會為同機乘客的健康造成嚴重威脅。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2366325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2366325&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=449fc973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2366325</a>"},{"pid":"08753e23f50638af6dbacf7f9860625f1ac54dc0","tid":2286382,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3720295943e297c430fde76f693a988d380f18e","tid":2286382,"uid":66087,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"越來越大牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19def58749daa779ce0e4403c9a207db02d2d3c7","tid":2286382,"uid":183758,"like":120,"dislike":3,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ByZj6wy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FByZj6wy.gif&h=87dddaa9&s={SIZE